    nAllCustOnLoad - only the sLoadId, nYear is used
    nSelectedCust - only the  naCustNos[*], nYear is used
    nSelectedCustOrd - only the  naCustNo[0], dtaOrdDT[*], nYear is used
    nAllCustInRegion - only the sRegionId, nYear is used
